+# Templates, Proof, and Receipts
+
+Templates are ION's type system for work.
+
+A template tells the assistant what kind of act is happening, what context is
+needed, what output is valid, what proof is owed, and what route follows.
+
+Portable GPT templates include:
+
+- project ingestion
+- source classification
+- decision receipt
+- package update
+- fresh-chat resume
+- diff proposal
+- friction event
+- human handoff
+
+Proof is lightweight in the GPT-only lane but must still be explicit:
+
+- what files/packages were considered
+- what was accepted vs proposed
+- what changed in the package
+- what remains open
+
+Receipts make accepted changes inheritable.

