+# Portable Package Import and Export
+
+The portable package is user-held continuity.
+
+Required structure:
+
+```text
+MANIFEST.json
+README_START_HERE.md
+PROJECT_BRIEF.md
+CURRENT_STATE.md
+SOURCE_MAP.yaml
+DECISION_LEDGER.md
+OPEN_QUESTIONS.md
+NEXT_ACTIONS.md
+RISKS_AND_ASSUMPTIONS.md
+USER_PREFERENCES.md
+
+context/
+receipts/
+diffs/
+friction/
+exports/
+raw_index/
+```
+
+Future chats inherit from the latest package.
+
+When exporting, preserve existing receipts and append new receipts. Do not
+silently rewrite history. If correcting a prior error, create a correction
+receipt.

